4205623.name: 6788 (Stella York)
4205623.notes: Exquisitely boho and perfectly casual, this wedding dress by bridal designer Stella York is a dreamy combination of comfort and style. Lace and delicate French tulle create a relaxed A-line silhouette made for magical moments. This dress is definitely for the fashion-forward boho bride with its really cool triangle back detail. Swiss dots are used on the bodice throughout the lace, making the pattern of the boho lace interesting and unique. A hint of twinkle has also been added to the lace to juxtapose the softness of the French tulle skirt. The triangle back is the real showpiece of this dress. Made of beaded shoestring straps, the geometric back demands to be seen.

4626905.notes: A simple and chic romance with bohemian inspiration, you'll fall in love with this floral lace mermaid wedding dress with glitter tulle from Stella York! The beaded shoestring straps are simple and modern, echoing the clean lines of the narrowed plunge and breathtaking open back detail. A thin layer of tulle falls gently over the hips of the fitted silhouette, adding soft volume. The growing floral pattern gently embellishes the bodice with a hint of silver sparkle-growing effortlessly over the curves and onto the layered skirt of glitter tulle for a shimmering finish.

4773028.name: D2835 (Essense of Australia)
4773028.notes: This modern wedding gown with dreamlike elements is something of another world! French lace brings the romance with this mixed-material bridal dress from Essense of Australia, placed atop tulle and embroidered laces to create the slightly sheer bodice with elegant high neckline and striking centerfront plunge. The beaded shoestring straps extend into a geometric, multi-banded back detail that is the epitome of fashion-forward style. Laces then trickle over strong, angular side cutouts for a stunning figure-falling onto the smooth stretch crepe for a negative space element. The dress transitions once again from the crepe skirt to the lace and tulle train, with unexpected scalloping and an out-of-this-world finish.

4816073.name: D2387
4816073.notes: Modern boho brides, take note, this sexy lace wedding dress from Essense of Australia was made for you! A plunging V-neckline is the focal point of this lace gown, highlighted perfectly with organic lace straps. This mix of French lace and cotton lace continues down through the sheer bodice, adding the perfect amount of sexiness to the style. From the bodice, the scrolling lace pattern continues down through the slight fit-and-flare silhouette, highlighted with latticework that makes it truly unique. Layers upon layers of tulle make the skirt of this gown appear light as air, and completely boho. The back of this wedding dress is highlighted with a scoop back, complete with organic lace trim. Illusion tulle gives a peek-a-boo look that extends into sexy sheer side cutouts. The back of this gown zips up beneath fabric-covered buttons.

5305530.notes: Laidback, casual and oh-so-chic, this beach wedding dress from Stella York was made for your oceanside celebration! The breathtaking, lace bodice of this gown features a light, organza underlay, adding to the illusion of a sheer bodice, while providing a bit of coverage. The illusion-lace neckline features organic lace detailing and an off-the-shoulder look, which only enhances the beachy feel. The back of this gown is highlighted with open, illusion tulle and lace detailing, giving it an effortlessly-romantic look. The light-as-air French tulle skirt extends effortlessly into a slight train. The back of this beach wedding dress zips up beneath Stella crystal buttons.
